  "text": "The relay uses compute-and-forward [CITATION_1] as relaying strategy and tries to decode L \u2212 1 linear combinationsv 1 , . . . ,v L\u22121 of the transmitted lattice codewords as shown in Fig. 2 . It uses a preprocessing matrix B to get the optimal signals prior to decoding. The achievable computation rate is then given by [CITATION_2] , [CITATION_3] ",
